data.description: If you are looking for a secluded private retreat, this is the one for you!! Tucked back in the trees of the neighborhood you will find this gorgeous sprawling 3,800 sq ft MOL home that features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, 2 living rooms, 2 dining areas, 3 car garage, a large deck that overlooks the fenced-in backyard and pond, spacious walk-out basement that includes a safe room and wine storage, and the perfect summertime oasis with a large pool, built in spa, and a spacious pergola. All sitting on 2.4 acres of wooded land. This home is one you won't want to miss, call today to schedule a showing!
